{"tid":1699772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致黃店老闆","createTime":"2019-11-08T07:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T13:41:08.000Z","uid":46984,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb480f073176507d1cdb9eb420d9d4af1b4e6fa","tid":1699772,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"致各黃店老闆<br />\n而家已經冇乜野輸 每個人都盡緊能力反抗緊<br />\n幫幫手開始帶頭罷工有冇得諗? <br />\n有第一間就有第二間架啦<br />\n全部人都等緊一個機會 只係唔想做第一個<br />\n<br />\n如果呢場運動輸左其實要走既就走 香港都唔再係香港 蝕曬所有野都唔係冇可能<br />\n如果羸左個少少損失跟本唔算得係乜野 真係黃既都唔會驚賺唔返<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇開錯..唔認同既由佢沉<br />\n香港人 <del>反抗</del> 報仇"},{"pid":"713bfbf22db3800bc055275bbc5f78baa984f728","tid":1699772,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:16:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1736fc34780aeba40ffe574dcfbbe1c95a9b1635","tid":1699772,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"每個人都好辛苦  每日睇到警暴到咁都冇辦法既無力感<br />\n有最好既方法大家一齊出少少力 <br />\n大罷工一定係最安全都大影響力 大家都可以係前線<br />\n<br />\n香港人 反抗"},{"pid":"9e80f2f7a6f90ec07f534e00ed7d91932c369416","tid":1699772,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:34:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f91df96a8361e7227d63d6e6766e2b7771f25e72","tid":1699772,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:03:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f34f628c8620218ecb87dce9b801f2cc7e6daf8","tid":1699772,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:35:19.000Z","msg":"你自己罷未"},{"pid":"7fed1c534f7e24f723edbbe0431913e9f42a4f7a","tid":1699772,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"一齊罷 香港人 反抗"},{"pid":"652c56512940923320fcf8a87f73584b6c7a79b1","tid":1699772,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"聽日大三罷<br />\n希望再推一推出一出力<br />\n<br />\n前線連命都唔要 <br />\n我聽日一定罷"}]}